data.description: Enjoy the million dollar view from your large, covered, front porch along with the deer, turkeys and other wildlife that call this property home! Approx. 3.5 acres with live water running the full length of the property only 3 miles from Powderhorn Ski Resort and approximately 45 minutes from Grand Junction. Easy highway access. Very close to skiing,hunting, fishing and biking. Numerous opportunities to add your personal touches to make this house your castle! New roof, gutters, windows, covered front porch, furnace/HVAC, Rinnai tank-less hot water heater, appliances, flooring, stucco, interior paint,  RV pad w/ 50 amp hookup, water and septic.
